<MILESTONE N="113, col. 3" UNIT="leaf">muchel heh&slong;cipe &amp; &slong;e &slong;eli freodom, &slong;chal
lihte &slong;e lahe in-to a monne&slong; &thorn;eowdom, &slong;wa
&thorn;at ha naue&eth; nawt freo of hire &slong;eluen, &amp; trukie,
