&thorn;i &thorn;at tu &slong;chulde&slong;t &thorn;in herte heouen
&thorn;iderward as tin heritage i&slong;, &amp; eor&eth;e forhohien.
Nim &yogh;eme hu &thorn;i&slong; un&thorn;eaw ne make&eth; <MILESTONE N="120" UNIT="leaf">&thorn;e
