&thorn;e&slong;elf &slong;ule&slong;t fore, &amp; &yogh;eue&slong;t
&thorn;in ahne <MILESTONE N="120, col. 2 " UNIT="leaf">dere bodi to tuken &slong;wa to wundre, &amp; fare
wi&eth; &slong;e &slong;chomeliche, wi&eth; &slong;wuch uncouerlich
