</P>
<P>&THORN;u &slong;ei&slong;t &thorn;at muche confort haue&eth; wif of
hire were, &thorn;at beo&eth; wel iGedered, &amp; ei&eth;er i&slong;
alle&slong; weis ipaied of o&eth;er.  &YOGH;ea.  Ah hit if &slong;elt
 
<PB N="39">
&slong;ene on eor&eth;e.  Beo nu &thorn;ah &slong;wuch: hare confort
&amp; hare delit, hwerin i&slong; hit al mea&slong;t, bute i
