hore o&eth;re&slong; uuel &slong;orhen &amp; &slong;iken.  Moni
&thorn;ing ham &slong;chal <MILESTONE N="120, back, col. 1" UNIT="leaf">twinnen &amp; tweinen, &thorn;at la&eth;
e&slong; leouie men; &amp; dea&eth;e&slong; dunt on ende, ei&eth;er
fram o&eth;er.  Swa &thorn;at ne be&eth; hit nane&slong; weis
